OL,3,CCouncils asked to investigate legal
OL,4,Cstatus of hotels housing asylum seekers
OL,6,FFour councils in Northern Ireland have
OL,7,Fbeen asked to investigate the legal
OL,8,Fstatus of hotels housing asylum
OL,9,Fseekers.
OL,11,FBelfast City Council is the latest to
OL,12,Fbe asked to launch an investigation.
OL,14,FIt comes after Unionist politicians
OL,15,Fquestioned if proper planning
OL,16,Fprocedures had been followed in the
OL,17,FArds and North Down Council, Antrim
OL,18,Fand Newtownabbey Council and Causeway
OL,19,FCoast and Glens council areas.
