OL,6,FIn a statement, Belfast City Council
OL,7,Fsaid: "The council has opened
OL,8,Fenforcement investigations into
OL,9,Falleged breaches of planning control
OL,10,Fby some hotels in the city, following
OL,11,Fa complaint.
OL,13,F"As these are live investigations, we
OL,14,Fcannot disclose any further
OL,15,Finformation."
OL,17,FA spokesperson for Causeway Coast and
OL,18,FGlens confirmed to UTV that there will
OL,19,Fbe inquiries made around the matters
OL,20,Fraised by the DUP and TUV.
