OL,6,FIn a statement they said: "The council
OL,7,Fhas received several queries relating
OL,8,Fto associated planning matters,
OL,9,Fhowever any enforcement cases are a
OL,10,Fconfidential matter."
OL,12,FEnforcement investigations have
OL,13,Falready begun into two other hotels
OL,14,Fwhich have both been the focus of anti-
OL,15,Fimmigration protests.
OL,17,FThe Marine Court in Bangor is used for
OL,18,Fasylum seeker accommodation but Ards
OL,19,Fand North Down Council said its
OL,20,Fplanning service did not receive a
OL,21,Fchange of use application.
