OL,3,CCouncils asked to investigate legal
OL,4,Cstatus of hotels housing asylum seekers
OL,6,FThe DUP have also asked if a similar
OL,7,Fapplication was submitted to Antrim
OL,8,Fand Newtownabbey Council, allowing
OL,9,FChimney Corner Hotel to house migrants.
OL,11,FIt comes after Epping Forest District
OL,12,FCouncil was granted a temporary
OL,13,Finjunction by the High Court on
OL,14,FTuesday that blocks asylum seekers
OL,15,Ffrom being housed at the Bell Hotel in
OL,16,Fthe Essex town.
OL,18,FEducation Minister Paul Givan claims
OL,19,Fwhat is happening in Northern Ireland
OL,20,Fis a symptom of a broken immigration
OL,21,Fsystem.
