OL,6,F"We are challenging the process.
OL,8,F"We will hold the UK government to
OL,9,Faccount and if hotels have been
OL,10,Frepurposed without getting the
OL,11,Fappropriate approvals, well, they need
OL,12,Fto follow due process, and we will
OL,13,Fchallenge the way in which those
OL,14,Fprocesses have been conducted, and
OL,15,Fthat is the right thing to do."
